channel.title: Project Perfection | Perfect Project Insanity Base | Re-written Skills | 508 Map
channel.description:
[CENTER][IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/vio64g.png[/img]
Firstly I'd love to say, I would love to spend much more time on this project
however I do not have any time anymore as I am now a developer for a fairly large growing server and cannot spend my time developing a project. please understand this is strictly a [B][U]BASE[/U][/B] and still needs work,
Thanks to whoever uses and puts effort into this will mean alot to me, I know this probably isn't as good as my other releases but atleast it's something ain't released in awhile however It's probably one of the best PI bases released to date. don't hate on this remark because I clearly said 'Probably', maybe something better out there but eh. enjoy to whoever uses.[/CENTER]
Server Features:
[ul][*]Better Firemaking [*]Better Cooking [*]Better Fishing [*]Better Mining [*]Better Prayer [*]Better Crafting [*]Better Fletching [*]Better Woodcutting [*]Full 63 wave jad [*]All Current PI Minigames (Apart from pest control needs a few fixes) [*]Clipped Following [*]Ancient Prayers (Need to fix headIcons)[/ul]
Client Features:
[ul][*]Cache Packed 602 Animations & Gfx [*]Cache Packed 508 Maps & Objects [*]Cache Packed 634 Items [*]Cache Packed 602 Npc's [*]Cache Packed 633 Characters [*]Toggling buttons changing HP Above head and name above head plus more [*]Perfect Hitmarks with fading [*]Perfect Orbs [*]Custom Interfaces[/ul]
Much more content lol just can't really remember ain't worked on this in like a week nor looked at it so had no purpose of keeping it on my desktop. :frustrated:
[IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/14lrpyu.png[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/mjsi1t.png[/img] [IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/1zfgz1g.png[/img] [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2lmq7v8.png[/img]
Download Links [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?sc0x43ko0m9zvcg]Server + Client.rar[/url] Cache is also in this please use the cache in the files as It's all been updates from the old one :/.
Credits: Wtf Ur Zerk 01053 Sanity Zanix Whoever Else I am missing that took part in this and/or Project insanity base.
Post any problems and I'll try me best to get around to everyone
Please if you really want to thank me thank the thread don't just say thanks. Cuz that's not proving your thankful. anyways don't know if that's allowed but oh well enjoy.
